00:12:42,974 --> 00:12:47,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't really care for doing it like this,</i>
<i>but I can't give up any road!</i></b></font>

137
00:12:47,844 --> 00:12:54,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What do I do?! Which way of winning</i>
<i>is the one that Ryosuke wants?</i></b></font>

138
00:12:54,524 --> 00:12:56,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The left, huh?!</i></b></font>

139
00:13:03,794 --> 00:13:06,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There's no way I'm lettin' you in front of me!</i></b></font>

140
00:13:06,364 --> 00:13:09,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have to save face in front of my peers, too!</i></b></font>

141
00:13:13,144 --> 00:13:17,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He'll go that far, will he?</i>
<i>If that's how he wants to play it...!</i></b></font>

142
00:13:21,084 --> 00:13:23,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There they are! They're coming, Iketani!</b></font>

143
00:13:30,424 --> 00:13:31,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

144
00:13:33,024 --> 00:13:36,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi's Eight-Six is gone!</i></b></font>

145
00:13:36,834 --> 00:13:42,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If you're thinking about riding it out into</i>
<i>the next race, that is a mistake, Fujiwara.</i></b></font>

146
00:13:45,574 --> 00:13:47,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't insist on a "pretty" victory.</i></b></font>

147
00:13:47,844 --> 00:13:52,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Having such self-centered</i>
<i>fixations will only limit oneself...</i></b></font>

148
00:13:52,544 --> 00:13:57,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>And being limited leads to the end of growth.</i></b></font>

149
00:13:57,584 --> 00:14:00,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If you feel resistance to pulling</i>
<i>ahead on the straightaway,</i></b></font>

150
00:14:00,524 --> 00:14:03,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that is hubris and dependency!</i></b></font>

151
00:14:03,254 --> 00:14:06,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How one wins does not require style!</i></b></font>

152
00:14:06,064 --> 00:14:08,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Go, Fujiwara!</i></b></font>

153
00:14:09,564 --> 00:14:11,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's gone!</i></b></font>

154
00:14:11,234 --> 00:14:13,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The Eight-Six is gone from my mirrors!</i></b></font>

155
00:14:13,534 --> 00:14:15,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That's impossible. It can't be!</i></b></font>

156
00:14:15,434 --> 00:14:18,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His headlights were right on me a second ago.</i></b></font>

157
00:14:18,704 --> 00:14:20,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't get it!</i></b></font>

158
00:14:32,554 --> 00:14:34,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What?!</i></b></font>

159
00:15:20,264 --> 00:15:25,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sakamoto got passed... The Eight-Six won!</b></font>

160
00:15:25,044 --> 00:15:26,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Impossible...</i></b></font>

161
00:15:26,704 --> 00:15:29,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He finished it in the first race?!</i></b></font>

162
00:15:42,294 --> 00:15:46,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I said it from the first, did I not?
A completely different mindset.</b></font>

163
00:15:46,324 --> 00:15:51,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The driver's job is to draw out a
car's latent potential to its very limits.</b></font>

164
00:15:51,834 --> 00:15:55,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If one were to describe the essence
of it, that's what it boils down to.</b></font>

165
00:15:55,004 --> 00:16:01,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Beyond racing fast, if there is one
key to beating an opponent's car,</b></font>

166
00:16:01,404 --> 00:16:05,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it is simply to turn this sentiment
into a weapon and to attack.</b></font>

167
00:16:05,314 --> 00:16:09,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This way of thought is what I wanted
you to experience in today's race.</b></font>

168
00:16:09,984 --> 00:16:14,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Telling you to recall Kyoichi's
methods meant not just his technique,</b></font>

169
00:16:14,324 --> 00:16:19,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but also included the
meaning of this psychology.</b></font>

170
00:16:19,324 --> 00:16:23,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Today's race was for the most part
decided until the halfway point.</b></font>

171
00:16:23,994 --> 00:16:27,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Good work sticking close to him, and not
being thrown off during that section.</b></font>

172
00:16:27,664 --> 00:16:30,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You did well. Just relax and enjoy yourself.</b></font>

173
00:16:30,404 --> 00:16:32,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The time trial has been cancelled.</b></font>

174
00:16:36,414 --> 00:16:38,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That turned out well, huh?</b></font>

175
00:16:38,944 --> 00:16:41,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... Did I just get praised?</b></font>

176
00:16:46,584 --> 00:16:51,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To be honest, I only sort of accept it.</b></font>

177
00:16:51,054 --> 00:16:54,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did I really do well in passing him like that?</b></font>

178
00:16:54,094 --> 00:16:57,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right up till the end, I really felt lost.</b></font>

179
00:16:57,764 --> 00:17:01,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought about doing nothing
and riding it out till the second race.</b></font>

180
00:17:01,434 --> 00:17:03,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a good thing you didn't.</b></font>

181
00:17:03,634 --> 00:17:08,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke would definitely
have gotten angry at you.</b></font>

182
00:17:08,644 --> 00:17:10,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really?</b></font>

183
00:17:10,074 --> 00:17:11,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course!</b></font>

184
00:17:11,714 --> 00:17:15,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no guarantee conditions would've
stayed the same for the second race.</b></font>

185
00:17:15,714 --> 00:17:19,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget, half the help
you got was from the rain.</b></font>

186
00:17:19,324 --> 00:17:23,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If it had stopped raining, it would've been
impossible to keep up with the Cappuccino.</b></font>

187
00:17:23,724 --> 00:17:26,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh... I guess you're right.</b></font>

188
00:17:26,794 --> 00:17:31,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you'd been racing on your own, you'd
be free to choose whichever you like,</b></font>

189
00:17:31,634 --> 00:17:35,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but right now you're racing
as a representative of D.</b></font>

190
00:17:35,404 --> 00:17:36,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't forget that.</b></font>

191
00:17:40,574 --> 00:17:45,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe it. How could you lose?!
And under these conditions!</b></font>

192
00:17:45,284 --> 00:17:49,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just can't believe it!
What the hell happened?!</b></font>

193
00:17:49,914 --> 00:17:53,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know. I don't get any of it.</b></font>

194
00:17:53,854 --> 00:17:58,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the straightaway right in front of
the goal, he just suddenly disappeared.</b></font>

195
00:17:58,094 --> 00:18:01,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He cleverly went into
the mirrors' blind spot, eh?</b></font>

196
00:18:01,664 --> 00:18:04,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If that were the case, I would've
noticed before he'd pulled alongside.</b></font>

197
00:18:04,094 --> 00:18:06,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I barely had time to go "Huh?"
before he was right there beside me.</b></font>

198
00:18:06,934 --> 00:18:10,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, get a hold of yourself.
What are you on about?</b></font>

199
00:18:10,704 --> 00:18:12,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're not some amateur!</b></font>

200
00:18:12,504 --> 00:18:16,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say what you like, but if I
don't get it, I don't get it!</b></font>

201
00:18:16,444 --> 00:18:19,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This has shocked <i>me</i> the most!</b></font>

202
00:18:19,044 --> 00:18:21,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, you've got a point.</b></font>

203
00:18:21,144 --> 00:18:25,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You guys couldn't beat
that Eight-Six either, right?</b></font>

204
00:18:25,224 --> 00:18:27,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, I've had enough of this.</b></font>

205
00:18:27,384 --> 00:18:30,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've completely lost confidence in myself.</b></font>

206
00:18:30,554 --> 00:18:33,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't look like I'll be
recovering from this for a while.</b></font>

207
00:18:35,534 --> 00:18:38,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's something fundamentally
different about that guy.</b></font>

208
00:18:42,004 --> 00:18:44,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's an incredible driver.</b></font>

209
00:18:46,904 --> 00:18:51,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, that blind attack in the middle
of the rain was really effective.</b></font>

210
00:18:51,714 --> 00:18:53,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The rain already made it hard to see,</b></font>

211
00:18:53,314 --> 00:18:57,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so to your opponent, I think it
really felt like you'd disappeared.</b></font>

212
00:18:59,854 --> 00:19:05,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke already said this, but that
tactic is a powerful weapon in a fight.</b></font>

213
00:19:05,894 --> 00:19:08,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You may be right...</b></font>

214
00:19:08,864 --> 00:19:13,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But personally, I don't think I
want to use it too frequently.</b></font>

215
00:19:13,104 --> 00:19:14,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd enjoy it too much.</b></font>

216
00:19:14,904 --> 00:19:16,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Enjoy it? You would?</b></font>

217
00:19:16,934 --> 00:19:19,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But it would come out spontaneously...</b></font>

218
00:19:19,844 --> 00:19:23,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If an opponent wouldn't open up
any road, I'd do it reflexively.</b></font>

219
00:19:23,414 --> 00:19:26,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Or if I got angry...</b></font>

220
00:19:26,614 --> 00:19:27,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah, there he is!</b></font>

221
00:19:27,844 --> 00:19:30,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

222
00:19:32,384 --> 00:19:35,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow, you really gave me a shock earlier!</b></font>

223
00:19:35,554 --> 00:19:39,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Somehow, I completely lost sight
of what your Eight-Six was doing!</b></font>

224
00:19:39,364 --> 00:19:41,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, us too.</b></font>

225
00:19:41,464 --> 00:19:43,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry 'bout that!</b></font>

226
00:19:44,864 --> 00:19:50,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I almost got hit by the Eight-Six, too!
I'll forgive ya this time, though.</b></font>

227
00:19:50,374 --> 00:19:53,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At least I'm not causing a scene...</b></font>

228
00:20:00,044 --> 00:20:02,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Levin! It can't be!</b></font>

229
00:20:02,314 --> 00:20:04,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's Wataru's Levin!</b></font>

230
00:20:04,284 --> 00:20:07,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. You just now noticed that?</b></font>

231
00:20:07,584 --> 00:20:11,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wataru's representing the
other team on the hillclimb.</b></font>

232
00:20:13,064 --> 00:20:17,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! What does that mean?
Don't tell me! Don't tell me!</b></font>

233
00:20:25,974 --> 00:20:29,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>K-Kazumi?</b></font>

234
00:20:37,254 --> 00:20:39,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi!</b></font>

235
00:20:40,324 --> 00:20:42,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's me! Me!</b></font>

236
00:20:44,754 --> 00:20:46,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki?</b></font>

237
00:20:58,604 --> 00:21:01,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The compressor!
You changed it to a supercharger?</b></font>

238
00:21:01,804 --> 00:21:06,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. After losing to that guy's Trueno last fall,</b></font>

239
00:21:06,484 --> 00:21:10,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I started feeling dissatisfied
with how my turbo was set up.</b></font>

240
00:21:10,554 --> 00:21:13,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd just finished putting the engine together</b></font>

241
00:21:13,654 --> 00:21:17,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and after thinking through a couple
of options, this is what I came up with.</b></font>

242
00:21:17,294 --> 00:21:22,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The supercharger's direct response is,
if anything, close to NA.</b></font>

243
00:21:22,734 --> 00:21:29,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It hasn't got the quirks of a turbo, and it
feels like I've put in a large-volume engine.</b></font>

244
00:21:29,474 --> 00:21:33,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This thing will be just the trick
for a tight course like today's.</b></font>

245
00:21:33,374 --> 00:21:35,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keep that in mind as you bring your A-game.</b></font>

246
00:21:35,914 --> 00:21:39,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I see. I'll have to do that.</b></font>

247
00:21:39,714 --> 00:21:44,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll friggin' show you what
having a turbo is all about.</b></font>

248
00:21:44,084 --> 00:21:48,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Line up your cars! The Levin
goes first, followed by the FD!</b></font>

249
00:22:17,754 --> 00:22:21,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, your task has
been set since last week.</b></font>

250
00:22:21,784 --> 00:22:24,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You understand, yes? Road surface conditions</b></font>

251
00:22:24,424 --> 00:22:26,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>are perfect for measuring its effectiveness.</b></font>

252
00:22:26,764 --> 00:22:31,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I know! Just watch
me out there, big brother.</b></font>

253
00:22:31,264 --> 00:22:32,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Very well.</b></font>

254
00:23:22,854 --> 00:23:24,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here we go!</b></font>

255
00:23:24,284 --> 00:23:26,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Starting in five seconds!</b></font>

256
00:23:26,524 --> 00:23:28,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Four! Three!</b></font>

257
00:23:28,994 --> 00:23:31,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two! One!</b></font>

258
00:23:31,524 --> 00:23:33,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Go!</b></font>

259
00:23:39,164 --> 00:23:42,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Awesome! For it to be a match
for the FD in the start dash,</b></font>

260
00:23:42,604 --> 00:23:45,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wataru's Levin must really be awesome!</b></font>

261
00:23:45,304 --> 00:23:48,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I installed a turbo in my Levin as well,
but this is completely different!</b></font>

262
00:23:48,844 --> 00:23:53,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My brother's Levin is rebuilt now,
and installed with a supercharger.</b></font>

263
00:23:53,444 --> 00:23:55,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A supercharger?</b></font>

264
00:23:55,314 --> 00:23:58,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He ended up blowing out his old engine.</b></font>

265
00:23:58,714 --> 00:24:03,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It looked like he really
hated losing to your friend.</b></font>

266
00:24:03,224 --> 00:24:06,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He put everything into his racing,
and really pushed himself.</b></font>

267
00:24:06,124 --> 00:24:09,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh. He did?</b></font>

268
00:24:09,394 --> 00:24:12,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, a supercharger is a bit unexpected.</b></font>

269
00:24:12,964 --> 00:24:18,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But he said it suits a car like the Eight-Six.</b></font>

270
00:24:19,844 --> 00:24:22,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My brother's very satisfied.</b></font>

271
00:24:22,474 --> 00:24:26,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He said that his racing power
has improved over his old turbo.</b></font>

272
00:24:46,934 --> 00:24:50,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Once we enter the low- to</i>
<i>mid-speed section coming up,</i></b></font>

273
00:24:50,404 --> 00:24:54,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>it doesn't matter how much power you</i>
<i>have, you won't be able to use it all.</i></b></font>

274
00:24:54,244 --> 00:24:57,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It will be a battle of driver vs. driver!</i></b></font>

275
00:24:57,074 --> 00:25:01,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's a street fight, where the winner is</i>
<i>the one with the strongest conviction!</i></b></font>

276
00:25:21,204 --> 00:25:25,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Senjou ni saita rose,</i>
<i>for the reason they don't know</i></b></font>

277
00:25:25,204 --> 00:25:29,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mae ni shika susumenai caterpillar</i>
<i>ga kyou mo fumitsubushita</i></b></font>

278
00:25:29,074 --> 00:25:33,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yo, hates and pain, nikushimi dake fuyashite</i></b></font>

279
00:25:33,384 --> 00:25:37,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hates and pain, sonna sesou, live eizou</i></b></font>

